fields.description:
If a workflow transition has a required field you have to exit GH and update that field. It will be great if withing the GH transition the screen will also have the required field in addition to the text fields.

*+NOTE+*:
{quote}
This will only support the required fields added by the [JIRA suite Utilisies plugin|http://confluence.atlassian.com/display/JIRAEXT/JIRA+Suite+Utilities]
{quote}
